name: Biaoqing TRON
description: A memecoin of the biggest meme in China known as Biaoqing, deployed and created on the Chinese chain of Justin Sun; Tron. A panda that represents different facial expressions - 'biaoqing' translates to 'facial expression' hence all the memes having different expressions. Biaoqing represents a strong cult like community due to the amount of support and backing this panda meme has not only in China but also world-wide.
